1972;;Hammer;;American;;Bruce D. Clark;;Fred Williamson, Bernie Hamilton, Vonetta McGee;;action;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hammer_(film);;B.J. Hammer is a boxer who rises up the ranks with help from the Mafia. However, Hammer doesn't realize that the help comes with a price: He is asked to throw a fight. Gangsters threaten to harm his girlfriend in an attempt to force him to go through with their plan. Hammer is forced to figure out a way to save his dignity and the life of his girlfriend, who has been kidnapped by gangsters.